details.description:
The player is a fumbling witch who bought a love potion to charm her crush. However, the witch didn't read the label and assumed it didn't work, carelessly throwing it away into the local town's well, causing the towns folk to be madly in love with her. She uses her magic powers to stop them from being charmed! Use upgrades for your magic to stop the wave of charmed towns folk. 

